kamus
    N, w, h, c, i: integer
    bmi, rata-rata, l: real
algoritma
    input(w, h, c, N)

        c=N+1(c/10) mod 2
        input(bmi)
        bmi= 10w/(h)*2 and l =bmi+(c/10)/2
        rataRata=(N+1, bmi, l)
        output(rataRata)
    endfor
endprogram

endprogram
